@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-z3gLpd7yknf1YoNbCzqRKc4qyor8gaKU1qmn+CShxbuBusANI9QpRohGBreCFkKxLhei6S9CQXFEbbKuqLg0DA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN"
          crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css//site.css" />
    <title>Heaven's Slice'</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <h1 class="fs-4">Heaven's Slice <i class="fa-solid fa-pizza-slice"></i></h1>
            <nav>
                <ul class="d-flex align-items-center py-2 my-2">
                    <li class="m-1 p-1">
                        <a href="/Home">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="m-1 p-1">
                        <a href="/Home/UserIndex">Our Products</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="m-1 p-1">
                        <a href="#">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between py-4">
            <div class="my-card-container card-one my-3 mt-0">
                <div class="overlay">
                    <div class="items"></div>
                    <div class="items head">
                        <p>Margherita</p>
                        <p class="ms-card-p">The most famous pizza which also represents best italy through its colors. The red tomato sauce, the green basil, the white cheese.</p>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                    <div class="items price">
                        <p class="new">€5</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="items cart">
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span>ADD TO CART</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="my-card-container card-two my-3 mt-0">
                <div class="overlay">
                    <div class="items"></div>
                    <div class="items head">
                        <p>4 Formaggi</p>
                        <p class="ms-card-p">
                            This pizza is the go to for cheese lovers. This one is a white pizza meaning there is no tomato sauce but insteade we have a blend of four different cheeses.
                        </p>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                    <div class="items price">
                        <p class="new">€6</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="items cart">
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span>ADD TO CART</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="my-card-container card-three my-3 mt-0">
                <div class="overlay">
                    <div class="items"></div>
                    <div class="items head">
                        <p>Capricciosa</p>
                        <p class="ms-card-p">An interesting pizza would be the Capricciosa. Ours is made with base of tomate sauce with different toppings such as ham, eggs, olives, artichokes and sausage.</p>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                    <div class="items price">
                        <p class="new">€6</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="items cart">
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span>ADD TO CART</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="my-card-container card-four my-3">
                <div class="overlay">
                    <div class="items"></div>
                    <div class="items head">
                        <p>Funghi e Prosciutto</p>
                        <p class="ms-card-p">
                            The pizzaiolo's personal favourite, this pizza is simple yet really tasty. Tomate sauce based, it topped with ham and fresh mushrooms.
                        </p>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                    <div class="items price">
                        <p class="new">€7</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="items cart">
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span>ADD TO CART</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="my-card-container card-five my-3">
                <div class="overlay">
                    <div class="items"></div>
                    <div class="items head">
                        <p>Marinara</p>
                        <p class="ms-card-p">Perhaps the most simple pizza we have, the marinara is made with tomate sauce, garlic oil and a touch of origan.</p>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                    <div class="items price">
                        <p class="new">€4.50</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="items cart">
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span>ADD TO CART</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="my-card-container card-six my-3">
                <div class="overlay">
                    <div class="items"></div>
                    <div class="items head">
                        <p>Mare e Monti</p>
                        <p class="ms-card-p">As its name implies (Sea and Earth), this pizza encapsulates the goodness that the land and the sea can offer. This transaltes into tomatoes, mushrooms, salmon, rucola</p>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                    <div class="items price">
                        <p class="new">€9</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="items cart">
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span>ADD TO CART</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container py-2 my-2 d-flex justify-content-center">
            <span>&#169; Bagnarola Roy inc</span>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>